'''Mesquitinha ''' (1902–1956) was a Portuguese-born Brazilian [[actor]] and [[film director]]. He appeared in a number of [[Chanchada]]s during the 1930s and 1940s including ''[[Hello, Hello, Brazil!]]'' (1935)<ref>Dennison & Shaw p.36</ref> and ''[[Samba in Berlin]]'' (1943).<ref>Dennison & Shaw p.71</ref>

==Selected filmography==

=== Director ===
* ''[[Onde Estás Felicidade?]]'' (1939)

===Actor===
* ''[[Estudantes]]'' (1935)
* ''[[Hello, Hello Brazil!]]'' (1935)
* ''[[Samba in Berlin]]'' (1943)

